      <Desc>GRASSTOPS: ACC ACTION'S GRASSTOPS PROGRAMMING INCLUDES COALITION BUILDING, THOUGHT LEADERSHIP, EDUCATION, AND ADVOCACY. IN 2025, ACTIVITIES INCLUDED HOSTING A CONGRESSIONAL FLY-IN, PARTICIPATING IN THE DEVELOPMENT OF LEGISLATION SUCH AS THE PATRIOT PARKS ACT, ANNOUNCING CONGRESSIONAL AND GUBERNATORIAL LEADERS AS 2025 ACC ACTION CHAMPIONS, AND CONDUCTING MEETINGS ON CAPITOL HILL RELATED TO CONSERVATION FUNDING FOR FARMERS AND RANCHERS, PERMITTING REFORM, AND FOREST MANAGEMENT.</Desc>
      <ProgSrvcAccomActy2Grp>
        <ExpenseAmt>332508</ExpenseAmt>
        <Desc>MARKETING &amp; COMMUNICATIONS: ACC ACTION'S COMMUNICATIONS BRIDGE A GRASSROOTS BASE WITH POLICY LEADERS THROUGH EARNED AND SOCIAL MEDIA EFFORTS. IN 2025, THIS RESULTED IN MORE THAN 2,000 MEDIA HITS AND MORE THAN HALF A BILLION SOCIAL MEDIA IMPRESSIONS.</Desc>
      </ProgSrvcAccomActy2Grp>
      <ProgSrvcAccomActy3Grp>
