        <Desc>GRASSROOTS: ACC ACTION'S GRASSROOTS PROGRAMMING INCLUDES EVENT SPONSORSHIPS, YOUTH CIVIC ENGAGEMENT INITIATIVES, EDUCATION, AND PUBLIC OUTREACH. IN 2025, 50 ACC ACTION ACTIVISTS PARTICIPATED IN A WASHINGTON, D.C., FLY-IN TO DISCUSS NUCLEAR ENERGY, CONSERVATION, AND PERMITTING REFORM WITH POLICYMAKERS. ACC ACTION ACTIVISTS ALSO SENT THOUSANDS OF LETTERS TO CONGRESS ON A RANGE OF POLICY ISSUES.</Desc>
